  "itemText": "<p>No delay in filing the complaint. The accused resides within the jurisdiction of this court, hence enquiry u/s.225 of BNSS is dispensed with. Heard. Perused the records. Satisfied that there is sufficient ground to proceed against the accused for the offence punishable u/s.138 of NI Act. Hence the court took cognizance of the aforesaid offence and the case is taken on file ST. Issue summons to accused.Take steps. For return of summons.29.06.2026.</p><p><br></p><p>Due to technical issue order passed on 16-05-2026 could not be uploaded. Hence the order of 16-05-2026 is uploaded today.</p>",
